澳門首例確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n澳門衞生局局長李展潤表示，該名康復患者治療費共3.4萬澳門元，離開澳門前沒有付款，她目前正申請豁免費用。李續指，外地人在澳門公共醫療機構治療需收取200%費用，根據傳染病防治法規定，她可按自身經濟狀況，以及病症對澳門公共利益影響等申請豁免費用，目前當局正審批申請，如不獲審批將被追收所有醫療費用。<br />\n<br />\n山頂醫院醫務主任李偉成表示，患者治療費用是按照她住院日數和藥物使用等標準收費，各人都有所不同，並非每宗個案都是3.4萬澳門元，即使內地患者已離開澳門，當局有多種方法追收費用，包括轉交財政局追收等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200206/mobile/bkn-20200206155810182-0206_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200206%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200206155810182-0206_00822_001.html&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOgjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=3479d0f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200206/mobile/bkn-20200206155810182-0206_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"国家對澳門咁多恩情，澳門人都唔會介意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506ac84d137a1de48b7b8437bdc44b27c5ce667e","tid":1869121,"uid":92476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7589eeb5fe37f73a9e6904eba12e9499c588246","tid":1869121,"uid":277186,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"澳門又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:47:47.000Z","msg":"唔使咁開心住，香港嘅情況無分別，大陸人係香港經常走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08668239f9d739b3df8e4e55779248cfc7697e8d","tid":1869121,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"微博瘋傳啦，香港仲有得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c087ece3bf871ae3c33e4e93465672a8842b962","tid":1869121,"uid":128160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21a6c25e0eb5d51e2fb8de64165886b4f968f33b","tid":1869121,"uid":51620,"like":211,"dislike":3,"score":208,"q